<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Playing with strangers is like doing that junior high trust test.  You know the one I'm talking about?  Where you stand with your back to your friend, and you fall, and you rely on them to catch you?<P>I'd say 90% of the time, the pick-up group members who you're trusting to catch you are either busy looting, talking to their guild, complaining they haven't gotten enough uber l00ts or dying.   <IMG SRC="tongue.gif" border="0"><P>It's *so* hard to find good people to group with!  I mean - Verant - please - let us have more than 20 in a friends list!   <IMG SRC="tongue.gif" border="0">  Most of the time I only see 2 of my 20 online.<P>Just my 2 velium bars.<P>--------------------<P>What sin has not been committed in the name of efficiency?<P>Occulis Rift <BR>Tarew Marr
