<FONT SIZE="1" color="#000000" face="Verdana, Arial">
posted April 12, 2001 11:01 AM &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
    &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=edit_post&f=7&t=001124&reply_num=000008&u="><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/eq/edit_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Edit/Delete Post"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=reply&f=7&t=001124&replyto=000008"><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/eq/quote_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Reply With Quote"></A>
