To Simryd<P>Ok well we can agree that the wizard is unballanced, and I will say broken is a subjective term. To tell the truth, I dont realy think they are broken either, simpley becuase it would take very little to make them ballanced. A few changes in the game would not only significantly impove the wizard class but all other casters as well. <P>1. ) lower resists of all post 50 mobs<BR>2. ) increase mana regen for all classes( post lvl 40 anyway by simply letting all casters get up to 300 in there meditation skill ).<BR>3. ) Increase the mana to damage ratio slightly for wizards, mags, and druids nukes. <P>These changes would make not only bring the mag and the wizard a lot closer to being ballanced classes but it would also improve the performance of all casters though increased mana regen and the enchanter would be even more valuable becuaes instead of cutting you mana regen time to 6 min the could cut it down to 3 min ( 6 min is still a prity long regen time  <IMG SRC="wink.gif" border="0"> ).
